65
00:26:51,593 --> 00:27:19,657
approve the records and the reports of committees by Councilor Mullen, seconded by Councilor Lemming. Mr. Clerk, please call the roll. Councilor Callahan? Councilor Lemming? Yes. Councilor Mullen? Yes. Councilor Scarpelli? Yes. Councilor Singh? Yes. Vice President Lazaro? Yes.

