Well, let's try it out and we'll table that one if we have to. On the motion of Council, I'm going to take communications from the Mayor out of order, seconded by? Seconded by Councilor Maloney. Ms. Clerk, please call the roll. Councilor Kelly? Yes. Councilor Levy? Yes. Councilor Maloney? Yes. Councilor Scarpelli? Yes.

