and rain date of May 17th. And this will be the CityTown Spring Softball Tournament hosted by Medford Youth Girls Softball. We do have the permits and it looks like we'll be welcoming teams from Arlington, Belmont, Boston, Cambridge, Charlestown, Everett, Medford, Somerville, Watertown, and Winchester. So thank you. On the motion to approve. Second. By Councilor Scarpelli. Seconded by? Lazzaro. Seconded by Vice President Lazzaro.

